data.description:
Listing agent is one of the owners.

Come inside this beautiful recently updated home in Lind Bohanon! This home is a 2BR/1BA, and features newer siding, newer flooring, updated kitchen and bathroom. This is a great home with great bones, unfinished basement allows for the imagination and equity builder. HUGE LOT to extend current garage, all fenced in for any pets. Great to have as a rental portfolio as well. 

Please allow 24hr notice on all showings.
